283
00:24:52,110 --> 00:24:53,540
No...

284
00:24:59,640 --> 00:25:02,380
I've wronged you, Mum, haven't I?

285
00:25:02,380 --> 00:25:05,650
Mum, just do me a favour...

286
00:25:05,650 --> 00:25:07,706
Before anyone else does it,

287
00:25:07,706 --> 00:25:08,722
Kill me!

288
00:25:08,722 --> 00:25:10,330
Why are you doing this? No!
-Kill me!

289
00:25:10,330 --> 00:25:12,591
What are you doing?
-Please, Mum -- I'm in great pain...

290
00:25:12,591 --> 00:25:15,953
