Kill me, Mum...
<i>Every bit of me afflicted with this eldritch malaise,</i>

293
00:25:22,429 --> 00:25:23,340
Calm down...
<i>Every bit of me afflicted with this eldritch malaise,</i>

294
00:25:23,340 --> 00:25:25,280
